<l n="ab" real="+++++--+++++-+-+---"><milestone unit="zone" n="1"/><lb n="1"/>ye dharmmā hetu-ppabhavā <space/> tesaṁ hetuṁ ta<milestone unit="zone" n="2"/>thāgato Avaca <space/></l>
<l n="cd">tesañ ca yo ni<milestone unit="zone" n="3"/>rodho <space/> Evaṁ-vādī mahā-saman<milestone unit="zone" n="4"/>o <g type="gomutraFinal"/></l>
